OL,7,FA sugar tax on pre-packaged milkshakes
OL,8,Fand lattes is expected to be announced
OL,9,Fby Wes Streeting on Tuesday ahead of
OL,10,Fthe Budget.
OL,12,FThe home secretary is expected to tell
OL,13,Fthe Commons that the government will
OL,14,Fend the exemption for milk-based
OL,15,Fdrinks from the existing tax on sugary
OL,16,Fdrinks.
OL,18,FThe move will affect packaged
OL,19,Fmilkshakes and coffees, but not drinks
OL,20,Fmade in cafes and restaurants.
