OL,7,FIt comes as Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,8,Fis expected to announce a series of
OL,9,Fsmaller tax rises to fill a #20
OL,10,Fbillion gap in public finances on
OL,11,FWednesday.
OL,13,FIt follows a government consultation
OL,14,Fon the issue, looking at removing the
OL,15,Fexemption for milk-based drinks while
OL,16,Fintroducing a "lactose allowance" to
OL,17,Faccount for the natural sugars in the
OL,18,Fmilk component of the drinks.
