OL,7,FMinisters have also been looking at
OL,8,Fremoving the exemption for milk
OL,9,Fsubstitute drinks with "added sugars"
OL,10,Fbeyond those sugars derived from the
OL,11,Fprincipal ingredient, such as oats or
OL,12,Frice.
OL,14,FThe sugar tax, also known as the soft
OL,15,Fdrinks industry levy (SDIL), is a tax
OL,16,Fon pre-packaged drinks such as those
OL,17,Fsold in cans and cartons in
OL,18,Fsupermarkets.
