OL,4,Cand lattes to be announced ahead of
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FIt applies to manufacturers and was
OL,8,Fintroduced by the Conservative
OL,9,Fgovernment in 2018 to help drive down
OL,10,Fobesity, including among children.
OL,12,FThe government has also been looking
OL,13,Fat reducing the maximum amount of
OL,14,Fsugar allowed in drinks from five
OL,15,Fgrams to four grams per 100ml, after
OL,16,Fwhich point they will be hit by the
OL,17,Flevy.
